【Skeleton Head】 It's curiosity. If you find an
unknown place on campus, it's natural to be

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's why I'm saying
this place is my laboratory.
【Skeleton Head】 That's because you came.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I see. However, this is
the end of this corridor.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That ladder over there
leads to the girls' dormitory room.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Although it's currently

【Skeleton Head】 Is this really just a corridor...
It would have been nice if there was a peephole or

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 What! This man...

【Masamune】 Sorry for getting in the way. I'll go
back now.

【Masamune】 By the way, why are you doing research
in a place like this?

【Masamune】 You could do magical research in the
facilities on campus, you know.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's because... I'm
researching tools to become able to use magic.
【Masamune】 Are you talking about magical tools?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Unlike conventional
magical tools, the current ones are designed to
assist with magic.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 What I am creating are
tools that generate magic.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 With this, anyone can
use magic.

【Tommy】 That's amazing! It means even ordinary
people can use it, right?

【Masamune】 But... there's no way the Samuel Church
would approve of something like that.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Even so... I will show
you that I can complete it.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 If you try using magic,
you should be able to understand its greatness.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 If that happens, people
from my homeland will also accept magic.
【Masamune】 Is there a reason for your homeland...?

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 There is, but it's not
something I need to discuss with you all.

【Skeleton Head】 Since we've come this far, let me
hear it. We've been talking up until now anyway.
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 ...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Well, if you want to
know, I suppose it's fine. It's actually a well-
known story in my homeland.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 The Prussian Kingdom
where I was born and raised, the majority of its
citizens are followers of the Samuel Church.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's why there is a
strong resistance against magic.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 If you use it in front
of people, it will be reported to the church
immediately.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That... includes even
members of the royal family.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 One time, the first
prince of the Prussian Kingdom used magic in front
of people.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 The rumors spread
quickly, and he received a huge backlash from the
citizens.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 The prince, who was
shocked by that, has been holed up in the castle
ever since.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 He was originally a
brave and intelligent person, but just because he
used magic...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's not a story that
can be forgiven.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 That's why I will make
the citizens recognize magic and bring back the
original, lively prince.
【Masamune】 What... You're a good kid, aren't you?
【Tommy】 Mmmhmm...
【Skeleton Head】 But, it won't change so easily.

【Leon】 Indeed. If we could resolve things so
easily, then nobody would have to go through all
this trouble.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Shut up! What do you
understand, you guys!
